These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, fantasy, animation
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, thai, dutch
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, r&b, rock
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, rat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, skateboarding, tennis
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, van
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
 2. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
 3. the thai is on the right of the fan of rock##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is the fan of r&b##1
 5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 6. the thai is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the argentine is the person watching musical movies##1
 8. the person driving the boat is the owner of the goldfish##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is between the owner of the goldfish and the person driving the van##2
10. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
11. the argentine is the owner of the rat##1
12. the dutch is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |         2          |     3      |
| Movie-Genre          | musical   | animation            | fantasy     |
| Nationality           | argentine | dutch | thai |
| Music-Genre   | disco      | rock               | r&b        |
| Pet           | rat        | chinchilla         | goldfish   |
| Sport         | tennis     | skateboarding      | golf       |
| Transport     | van        | train              | boat       |

