.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, lemonade, milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, chestnut, white
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, davidoff, pall-mall
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, trance
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, snake
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the person who likes ivory is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 3. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
 4. the person who likes white is the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person who likes ivory and the fonseca-smoker##2
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who likes chestnut and the person driving the skateboard##2
 7. the person drinking milk is the owner of the mouse##1
 8. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 9. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left or far right##3
10. the fan of trance is the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | lemonade | milk        |
| Color          | chestnut   | white    | ivory        |
| Cigar   | fonseca    | davidoff | pall-mall |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | ambient  | r&b         |
| Pet           | snake    | hedgehog | mouse       |
| Transport     | subway   | trike    | skateboard  |

