.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, skiing, rowing
There 3 different types of food: apricot, eggplant, raspberry
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, gardening, magic-tricks
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, pakistani, malaysian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, mystery, western
3 different pets are kept: cat, pony, rat
 1. the egyptian is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skiing##3
 2. the malaysian is the person eating raspberry##1
 3. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person eating apricot is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the owner of the pony##2
 6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is in an odd position##4
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 9. the malaysian is on the far right##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the pakistani##1
12. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
13. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |      3       |
| Sport      | skiing        | climbing     | rowing          |
| Food          | eggplant     | apricot | raspberry    |
| Hobby         | gardening    | baking  | magic-tricks |
| Nationality           | pakistani | egyptian    | malaysian    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery      | western | fantasy      |
| Pet           | cat          | rat     | pony         |

