.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, gospel, soul
City: marseilles, colone, boston
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, april, september
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of d&b is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's hobby is reading##2
 6. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
 7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
 8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
10. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
11. the person traveling to colone is on the far left or far right##3
12. the person who's hobby is reading is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | sprite      | fanta        |
| Hobby         | reading   | cooking     | magic-tricks |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | documentary | disaster     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | d&b         | soul         |
| City   | marseilles   | boston     | colone      |
| Birthday         | december  | september     | april         |

