 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
 3. the cottage house is the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the owner of the rat is the fan of jazz##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the freelancer##1
 6. the police-officer is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 7. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
 8. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the owner of the rat is on the far left##1
11. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
12. the fan of electronic is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
