.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-4-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, card-games, hiking
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, november, december
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, daisy, orchid
There are 3 different nationalities: british, german, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skiing, tennis
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the nigerian##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the nigerian##2
3. the british is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who growstulip is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
8. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person drinking juice##2
9. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |         2          |      3      |
| Beverage      | juice    | iced-tea           | 7up         |
| Hobby         | hiking   | baking             | card-games  |
| Birthday           | december  | november | september |
| Flower   | tulip      | daisy              | orchid      |
| Nationality   | nigerian | german             | british     |
| Sport         | skiing   | handball           | tennis      |

